)"},"H8329":{"id":"H8329","lemma":"שֶׁרֶשׁ","translit":"Sheresh","pron":"sheh'-resh","derivation":"the same as H8328 (שֶׁרֶשׁ);","strongs_def":"Sheresh, an Israelite","kjv_def":"Sharesh."},"H8330":{"id":"H8330","lemma":"שֹׁרֶשׁ","translit":"shôresh","pron":"sho'-resh","derivation":"(Aramaic) corresponding to H8328 (שֶׁרֶשׁ)","strongs_def":"{a root (literally or figuratively)}","kjv_def":"root.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"root(3x)"},"H8331":{"id":"H8331","lemma":"שַׁרְשָׁה","translit":"sharshâh","pron":"shar-shaw'","derivation":"from H8327 (שָׁרַשׁ);","strongs_def":"a chain (as rooted, i.e. linked)","kjv_def":"chain. Compare H8333 (שַׁרְשְׁרָה).","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"chain(1x)"},"H8332":{"id":"H8332","lemma":"שְׁרֹשׁוּ","translit":"shᵉrôshûw","pron":"sher-o-shoo'","derivation":"(Aramaic) from a root corresponding to H8327 (שָׁרַשׁ);","strongs_def":"eradication, i.e. (figuratively) exile","kjv_def":"banishment.","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"banishment(1x)"},"H8333":{"id":"H8333","lemma":"שַׁרְשְׁרָה","translit":"sharshᵉrâh","pron":"shar-sher-aw'","derivation":"from H8327 (שָׁרַשׁ) (compare H8331 (שַׁרְשָׁה));","strongs_def":"a chain; (architectural) probably a garland","kjv_def":"chain.","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"chain(7x)"},"H8334":{"id":"H8334","lemma":"שָׁרַת","translit":"shârath","pron":"shaw-rath'","derivation":"a primitive root;","strongs_def":"to attend as a menial or worshipper; figuratively, to contribute to","kjv_def":"minister (unto), (do) serve(-ant, -ice, -itor), wait on.","pos":"verb","usage":"serve(8x), servant(5x), service(3x), servitor(1x), waited(1x)"},"H8335":{"id":"H8335","lemma":"שָׁרֵת","translit":"shârêth","pron":"shaw-rayth'","derivation":"infinitive of H8334 (שָׁרַת);","strongs_def":"service (in the Temple)","kjv_def":"minister(-ry).","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"ministry(1x), minister(1x)"},"H8336":{"id":"H8336","lemma":"שֵׁשׁ","translit":"shêsh","pron":"shaysh","derivation":"or (for alliteration with H4897 (מֶשִׁי)) 